==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lettering
<hw>Let"ter*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or business
of making, or marking with, letters, as by cutting or
painting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The letters made; <as>as, the <ex>lettering</ex> of
a sign</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Letterless</ent>⟦br⟧
